v0.x.0
* Now support environment specific config files
* Enable execution of SQL from files with db.shell command
* Register step classes with decorator instead of subclass
* Allow instances of step classes instead of just classes
* New fast-forward command (ff)
* Allow migrating an individual step from the command line

v0.2.1
* More error checking to avoid migrations out of order
* Fail on rollback drop b/c it cannot be dropped
* Updated setup.py for new file structure

v0.2.0
* Changed phases to add, simdrop and drop
* Add better tests to solidify behavior and error cases

v0.1.0
* Initial version
* Works for deploying changes but isn't great

